We are hiring a Full-Stack Web Developer to build and maintain modern web applications.
Required: strong JavaScript, TypeScript, HTML, CSS, React.js, Node.js, and Express.js experience.
You will design responsive user interfaces, RESTful APIs, and reusable React components.
